The paper deals with multimedia data encryption, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also focuses on security and encryption algorithms, which can be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of H.264 compression and AES encryption suggests that the paper may also fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the application of the proposed algorithm in military training indicates that the paper may also belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
